original: Munktell, Theo f ron Nils Thor sten s-son, tandläkare, Borås, f. 18/5/07 i Torshälla av prov:iäk. Thorsten M. o. Signe Strömbom. G. 32 m. Karin Magnusson. Barn: Eva f. 36, Hans 40, Agneta 44. — Stud:ex. i Umeå 26, tandi:-kand. 28, tandl. 31. Prakt, i Borås sed. 31.
translated:
Munktell, Theo, born Nils Thorsten's son, dentist, from Borås. Born on May 18, 1907, in Torshälla, to legitimate parents Thorsten M. and Signe Strömbom. Married to Karin Magnusson in 1932. Children: Eva, born in 1936, Hans in 1940, Agneta in 1944. 

Education: Passed student's maturity exam in Umeå in 1926. Enrolled in dental studies in 1928, graduated as a dentist in 1931. Practicing in Borås since 1931.
